《'''怦怦心跳'''》（{{lang-en|"Boom Clap"}}<ref>{{cite AV media |title=CHARLI XCX 酷娃恰莉 - BOOM CLAP 怦怦心跳 (華納 official 高畫質 HD 官方完整版MV) |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qSvoGGqZjX4 |language=en |deadurl=yes |date=2015-03-02 |accessdate=2020-02-16 |publisher=華納音樂 Warner Music Taiwan YouTube 頻道 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200926213346/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qSvoGGqZjX4 |archivedate=2020-09-26 }}{{Wayback|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qSvoGGqZjX4 |date=20200926213346 }}</ref>），是英国女歌手[[查莉·XCX|查莉·XCX]]的一首歌曲，收录于她的录音室专辑《{{le|爛咖|Sucker (album)}}》<ref>{{cite web|url=http://pitchfork.com/news/56813-charli-xcx-pushes-album-back-due-to-success-of-bloom-clap/|title=Charli XCX Pushes Album Back Due to Success of "Boom Clap"|work=Pitchfork|accessdate=2015-05-03|archive-date=2014-09-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140923160824/http://pitchfork.com/news/56813-charli-xcx-pushes-album-back-due-to-success-of-bloom-clap/|dead-url=no}}</ref>与电影《[[星运里的错|星运里的错]]》电影原声带中。该首歌曲在[[英国单曲榜|英国单曲榜]]最高排位第六，在美国[[告示牌百强单曲榜|告示牌百强单曲榜]]最强排位第八。该首歌曲也以[[追加下载内容|追加下载内容]]的形式收录于游戏《{{tsl|en|Just Dance 2015|舞力全开2015}}》中。<ref>{{Cite web|url = https://twitter.com/justdancegame/status/525388983929274368/photo/1|title = ps boom clap will be on #justdance2015 !!|date = |accessdate = |website = |publisher = |last = |first = |archive-date = 2016-03-04|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304203036/https://twitter.com/justdancegame/status/525388983929274368/photo/1|dead-url = no}}</ref>

==歌曲背景==
这首歌由[[查莉·XCX|查莉·XCX]]、Fredrik Berger、{{le|Patrik Berger|Patrik Berger (record producer)}}和Stefan Gräslund制作，其计划收录于查莉·XCX的第二张专辑《{{tsl|en|True Romance (Charli XCX album)|真浪漫}}》（{{lang-en|''True Romance''}}）中，并提供给歌手及演员[[希拉蕊·朵芙|希拉蕊·朵芙]]。但朵芙的经纪人拒绝了她的请求，于是她将这首歌提供给电影《[[星运里的错|星运里的错]]》的电影原声带作为电影中的一首插曲使用。在之后的一次采访中，希拉蕊·朵芙表示自己对查莉XCX给她提供了这首歌一事毫不知情。如果她知道的话，她会接受这首歌。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.popjustice.com/thenews/hilary-duff-bloody-loves-boom-clap-and-didnt-know-shed-turned-it-down/129532/|title=Hilary Duff bloody loves 'Boom Clap' and didn't know she'd turned it down - Popjustice|work=Popjustice|access-date=2015-05-03|archive-date=2019-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190629080606/https://www.popjustice.com/thenews/hilary-duff-bloody-loves-boom-clap-and-didnt-know-shed-turned-it-down/129532/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

